SELECT 'ChangeDelivery' || '::' || "Delivery_Changes"."ID"  AS "ID",
       "Delivery"."ID"                                      AS "Delivery",
       "Delivery_Changes"."Time"                            AS "Time",
       "Delivery_Changes"."ChangedBy"                       AS "ExecutedBy",
       "Delivery_Changes"."Attribute"                       AS "ChangedAttribute",
       "Delivery_Changes"."ExecutionType"                   AS "ExecutionType",
       "Delivery_Changes"."OldValue"                        AS "OldValue",
       "Delivery_Changes"."NewValue"                        AS "NewValue"
FROM "o_custom_Delivery" AS "Delivery"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_Delivery" AS "Delivery_Changes"
        ON "Delivery"."ID" = "Delivery_Changes"."ObjectID"
            AND "Delivery_Changes"."Attribute" IN (
                'TotalWeight',
                'SalesDistrict',
                'WeightUnit',
                'PlannedPickingDate',
                'DeliveryType',
                'DeliveryDate',
                'NetWeight',
                'ProofOfDeliveryDate',
                'Route',
                'SalesOrganization',
                'VolumeUnit',
                'Volume'
            )
WHERE "Delivery_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
